---
// InteractiveCards.astro

const products = [
  { name: "CRYSTALIN", link: "https://www.crystalin.fit/" },
  { name: "FIXINOL", link: "https://www.fixinol.fit/" },
  { name: "LIPOXIN", link: "https://www.lipoxin.fit/" },
  { name: "LIFETONE", link: "https://www.lifetone.fit/" },
  { name: "MAXIFLEX", link: "https://www.maxiflex.fit/" },
  { name: "ULTRAVEN", link: "https://www.ultraven.fit/" },
  { name: "ANDROMAX", link: "https://www.andromax.fit/" },
];
---

<section class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
  <h2 class="text-center text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-12">
    ¿Cómo podemos <span class="font-semibold text-[#1B365D]"
      >ayudarte a mejorar tu vida</span
    >?
  </h2>

  <div
    class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-5 gap-6"
  >
    <!-- Tarjeta 1 -->
    <div class="relative h-64 group perspective">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#FF6100] rounded-xl p-6 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-center text-xl font-medium transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-pointer transform-style preserve-3d group-hover:opacity-0 group-hover:scale-95"
      >
        ¿Quieres dormir mejor?
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col items-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out shadow-lg transform scale-90 group-hover:scale-100"
      >
        <div class="flex-1 flex items-center">
          <p class="text-center text-neutral-dark text-base">
            Sabías que el 6,7% de la población española está oficialmente
            diagnosticada de ansiedad
          </p>
        </div>
        <a
          href={products[0].link}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="mt-4 bg-[#FF6100] text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-[#E65600] transition-colors text-base w-full max-w-[200px] text-center inline-block no-underline"
        >
          Quiero dormir mejor
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tarjeta 2 -->
    <div class="relative h-64 group perspective">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#FF6100] rounded-xl p-6 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-center text-xl font-medium transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-pointer transform-style preserve-3d group-hover:opacity-0 group-hover:scale-95"
      >
        ¿Necesitas un plus de energía?
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col items-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out shadow-lg transform scale-90 group-hover:scale-100"
      >
        <div class="flex-1 flex items-center">
          <p class="text-center text-neutral-dark text-base">
            La falta de energía puede afectar significativamente tu calidad de
            vida
          </p>
        </div>
        <a
          href={products[6].link}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="mt-4 bg-[#FF6100] text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-[#E65600] transition-colors text-base w-full max-w-[200px] text-center inline-block no-underline"
        >
          Quiero más energía
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tarjeta 3 -->
    <div class="relative h-64 group perspective">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#FF6100] rounded-xl p-6 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-center text-xl font-medium transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-pointer transform-style preserve-3d group-hover:opacity-0 group-hover:scale-95"
      >
        ¿Quieres cuidar tu salud digestiva y evitar que tu estómago te pese?
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col items-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out shadow-lg transform scale-90 group-hover:scale-100"
      >
        <div class="flex-1 flex items-center">
          <p class="text-center text-neutral-dark text-base">
            Una buena digestión es clave para tu bienestar general
          </p>
        </div>

        <a
          href={products[6].link}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="mt-4 bg-[#FF6100] text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-[#E65600] transition-colors text-base w-full max-w-[200px] text-center inline-block no-underline"
        >
          Mejorar mi digestión
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tarjeta 4 -->
    <div class="relative h-64 group perspective">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#FF6100] rounded-xl p-6 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-center text-xl font-medium transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-pointer transform-style preserve-3d group-hover:opacity-0 group-hover:scale-95"
      >
        ¿Quieres mejorar tu salud íntima?
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col items-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out shadow-lg transform scale-90 group-hover:scale-100"
      >
        <div class="flex-1 flex items-center">
          <p class="text-center text-neutral-dark text-base">
            Tu salud íntima merece atención y cuidado especial
          </p>
        </div>
        <a
          href={products[6].link}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="mt-4 bg-[#FF6100] text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-[#E65600] transition-colors text-base w-full max-w-[200px] text-center inline-block no-underline"
        >
          Cuidar mi salud íntima
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tarjeta 5 -->
    <div class="relative h-64 group perspective">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#FF6100] rounded-xl p-6 flex items-center justify-center text-white text-center text-xl font-medium transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out cursor-pointer transform-style preserve-3d group-hover:opacity-0 group-hover:scale-95"
      >
        ¿Te gustaría mejorar tus niveles de estrés y ansiedad?
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 bg-white rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col items-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out shadow-lg transform scale-90 group-hover:scale-100"
      >
        <div class="flex-1 flex items-center">
          <p class="text-center text-neutral-dark text-base">
            El manejo del estrés es fundamental para una vida saludable
          </p>
        </div>
        <a
          href={products[6].link}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="mt-4 bg-[#FF6100] text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-[#E65600] transition-colors text-base w-full max-w-[200px] text-center inline-block no-underline"
        >
          Reducir mi estrés
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .perspective {
    perspective: 1000px;
  }

  .transform-style {
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
  }
</style>
